"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-left:29px\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;times new roman&quot;; font-size: 18px;\">Wen X, Shu Y, Qu D, Wang Y, Cui Z, Zhang X*, Chen R*. Associations of bullying perpetration and peer victimization subtypes with preadolescent’s suicidality, non-suicidal self-injury, neurocognition, and brain development. </span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;times new roman&quot;; font-size: 18px;\">BMC Medicine</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;times new roman&quot;; font-size: 18px;\">, 2023 Apr 12;21(1):141.</span></p></li>\n <li><p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-left:29px\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;times new roman&quot;; font-size: 18px;\">Qu D, Wen X, Liu B, Zhang X, He Y, Chen D, Duan X, Yu J, Liu D, Zhang X, Ou J, Zhou J, Cui Z, An J, Wang Y, Zhou X, Yuan T, Tang J, Yue W*, Chen R*. Non-suicidal self-injury in Chinese population: a scoping review of prevalence, method, risk factors and preventive interventions. </span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;times new roman&quot;; font-size: 18px;\">The Lancet Regional Health–Western Pacific</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;times new roman&quot;; font-size: 18px;\">. 2023, 100794.</span></p></li>\n <li><p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-left:29px\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;times new roman&quot;; font-size: 18px;\">Duan, Y., Xu, S</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;times new roman&quot;; font-size: 18px;\">*</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;times new roman&quot;; font-size: 18px;\">., Wang, Y., Zhang, Y., Wang, Y</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;times new roman&quot;; font-size: 18px;\">*</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;times new roman&quot;; font-size: 18px;\">., &amp; Chen, R</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;times new roman&quot;; font-size: 18px;\">*</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;times new roman&quot;; font-size: 18px;\">. (2022). Blind box over-engagement and suicide risk among adolescents and young adults